after: Icelandair Group operates a number of other subsidiary airlines.
Loftleidir-Icelandic operates on the international aircraft leasing market. The company leases out 4 Boeing 757-200s, 3 Boeing 767-300s, 1 Boeing 737-700 and 2 Boeing 737-800s.[87]
